 />\n但原來六成只係有20客, 即係原來徥 20 / 60% = 33個客入票<br />\n<br />\n水票驚人<br />\n<br />\n(值得一提, 哩個盤美聯做獨家, 布生無得吹係其它行家有水票)<br />\n<br />\n總結:<br />\n代理行水票情況猖獗, 33個客可變大十倍以上, 大家信代理吹水嘅請繼續。什麼超額X倍嘅, 信不信由你"},{"pid":"44ac1fc19f78b59b1ae2a53d207d79913d478399","tid":907184,"uid":112720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T15:15:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n剛需"},{"pid":"345060d836ed9f0ab4f4985d4325fe718ed9dd33","tid":907184,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T15:17:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af495a24c1ec35d79177a087013d31d46c4b0c51","tid":907184,"uid":159313,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T16:05:58.000Z","msg":"版主幾快手del post<br />\n近排好多post都係咁<br />\n愈係咁證明個市已陷家鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c86635558fb4d6d5bc3c5232ba94c9f82e766d","tid":907184,"uid":62935,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"af495a24c1ec35d79177a087013d31d46c4b0c51","tid":907184,"uid":159313,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T16:05:58.000Z","msg":"版主幾快手del post<br />\n近排好多post都係咁<br />\n愈係咁證明個市已陷家鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T16:09:57.000Z","msg":"跌吉班好版板主 真係好撚快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffec786ade1dd7ab4b8c3db08be239e7c4e6a65","tid":907184,"uid":62935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"345060d836ed9f0ab4f4985d4325fe718ed9dd33","tid":907184,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T15:17:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T16:10:35.000Z","msg":"可以一個月後參考呢個盤有幾多撻訂<img src=\"/assets/fa